Me passa o Narcan.

226
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,153
Quê?

227
00:17:31,236 --> 00:17:32,237
É tarde demais.

228
00:17:32,321 --> 00:17:33,363
Passe o Narcan agora!

229
00:17:34,990 --> 00:17:36,074
Ei.

230
00:17:36,450 --> 00:17:37,534
Ei.

231
00:17:38,785 --> 00:17:39,828
Dr. Moore.

232
00:17:49,213 --> 00:17:50,214
Ei!

233
00:17:51,548 --> 00:17:52,841
Por que tentou me expurgar?

234
00:17:52,925 --> 00:17:54,259
Ivory Road.

235
00:17:54,343 --> 00:17:55,385
-Quê?
-Ivory Road.

236
00:17:56,887 --> 00:17:58,138
Ivory Road...

237
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,238
O Tommy já voltou?

238
00:18:32,322 --> 00:18:34,032
-Não sei dele.
-Merda.

239
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:40,204
Tive que pagar a conta da minha mãe,
vai sair da minha parte.

240
00:18:40,288 --> 00:18:41,539
Como ela está?

241
00:18:41,623 --> 00:18:42,624
Igual.

242
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:45,335
