247
00:18:55,553 --> 00:18:57,847
Ela me deu codeína para a dor, então...

248
00:18:58,514 --> 00:18:59,557
Merda.

249
00:18:59,974 --> 00:19:00,975
Quê?

250
00:19:01,059 --> 00:19:03,227
Sem a mala do Tommy, deu 200.

251
00:19:03,311 --> 00:19:05,480
